IN RE: COMMITTEE ON BAR ADMISSIONS CFN-845260 NO. 2018-BA-0729 Supreme Court of Louisiana. June 15, 2018

BAR ADMISSIONS PROCEEDING

PER CURIAM

After reviewing the evidence and considering the law, we conclude petitioner is eligible to be admitted to the practice of law in Louisiana.

ADMISSION GRANTED.

GUIDRY, J., would remand to the Panel on Character and Fitness to conduct an investigation and appoint a commissioner.

GENOVESE, J., would remand to the Panel on Character and Fitness to conduct an investigation and appoint a commissioner.
